500}} lb\t|| 120,152&nbsp;lb\t|| 4,602&nbsp;nmi{{efn|name=4pax}}\t|| 446 kn\t|| {{#expr:44240/4602round2}} lb\n|-\n| [[Boeing Business Jet|BBJ MAX]]-7\t|| 19-172\t|| 116.7&nbsp;ft\t|| 117.8&nbsp;ft\t|| 85.5&nbsp;ft\t|| 11.6&nbsp;ft\n| 2 [[CFM LEAP]]\t|| {{#expr:2*29300}} lb\t|| 177,000&nbsp;lb\t|| 7,000&nbsp;nmi\t|| \t||\n|-\n| [[Boeing Business Jet|BBJ MAX]]-8\t|| 19-189\t|| 129.7&nbsp;ft\t|| 117.8&nbsp;ft\t|| 98.5&nbsp;ft\t|| 11.6&nbsp;ft\t|| 2 [[CFM LEAP]]\t|| {{#expr:2*29300}} lb\t|| 181,200&nbsp;lb\t|| 6,640&nbsp;nmi\t|| \t||\n|-\n| [[Airbus Corporate Jets|ACJ]]319\t|| 19-156\t|| 111.0&nbsp;ft\t|| 111.8&nbsp;ft\t|| 78.0&nbsp;ft\t|| 12.2&nbsp;ft\n| 2 [[CFM56]]\t|| {{#expr:2*27000}} lb\t|| 168,650&nbsp;lb\t|| 6,002&nbsp;nmi\t|| 442 kn\t|| {{#expr:65558/6002round2}} lb\n|-\n| [[Boeing Business Jet|BBJ MAX]]-9\t|| 19\u2013220\t|| 138.3&nbsp;ft\t|| 117.8&nbsp;ft\t|| 107.2&nbsp;ft\t|| 11.6&nbsp;ft\t|| 2 [[CFM LEAP]]\t|| {{#expr:2*29300}} lb\t|| 194,700&nbsp;lb\t|| 6,515&nbsp;nmi\t|| \t|| \n|}\n\n==See also==\n{{commonscat|Business jets}}\n* [[Very light jet]]\n* [[Air transports of heads of state and government]]\n* [[Supersonic business jet]]\n\n== Notes ==\n{{notelist}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n\n<ref name=FMvlj>{{cite magazine |url= http://www.flyingmag.com/tags/very-light-jet |title= Very light jets |magazine= [[Flying (magazine)|Flying]]}}</ref>\n<ref name=FMlj>{{cite magazine |url= http://www.flyingmag.com/tags/light-jets |title= Light jets |magazine= [[Flying (magazine)|Flying]]}}</ref>\n<ref name=FMmsj>{{cite magazine |url= http://www.flyingmag.com/tags/mid-size-jets |title= Mid-size jets |magazine= [[Flying (magazine)|Flying]]}}</ref>\n<ref name=FMsmsj>{{cite magazine |url= http://www.flyingmag.com/tags/super-mid-size-jets |title= Super mid-size jets |magazine= [[Flying (magazine)|Flying]]}}</ref>\n<ref name=FMhj>{{cite magazine |url= http://www.flyingmag.com/tags/heavy-jets |title= Heavy jets |magazine= [[Flying (magazine)|Flying]]}}</ref>\n<re